{"tid":2089083,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"BNO平權-建議有心過外國但英文又唔好既 即該係香港考返個車牌先","createTime":"2020-07-01T13:18:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T00:54:06.000Z","uid":40521,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"9df900b24260f34ec3f0bbd79b0e0d646deddff7","tid":2089083,"uid":40521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:18:47.000Z","msg":"成日有人講 係外國無車就好似跛咗隻腳  我覺得岩一半啦，平時有車係方便d既但又唔可以話無左佢唔得 <br />\n但但但係...當係冬天或者落雨果時你就知道佢既重要性 由其你去買完野又無車 凍冰冰拎住啲嘢企係街度等車都攞命<br />\n<br />\n所以如果你英文唔好要係外國考車牌筆試會有d難度<br />\n係外國養部車只係香港既十分一價錢<br />\n殘殘地幾千蚊港紙都有架 再用佢去做外賣仔 兩三個禮拜就可以回本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以車牌係外國係必須 快快去考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c7tAYfz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc7tAYfz.png&h=c5f75913&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db5f9b66b5a7f2fa7ea3afae3ce471a91c7cf509","tid":2089083,"uid":248493,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:19:33.000Z","msg":"咪on9啦，英國之嘛，洗撚揸車咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f47e9750039ea7d6b76006c17502db8a0b21e9ee","tid":2089083,"uid":127425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:20:49.000Z","msg":"外國做外賣仔唔係揸單車多咩"},{"pid":"d16ed9bb556363dafa55b6109c8e4a4601ed05a6","tid":2089083,"uid":268053,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"db5f9b66b5a7f2fa7ea3afae3ce471a91c7cf509","tid":2089083,"uid":248493,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:19:33.000Z","msg":"咪on9啦，英國之嘛，洗撚揸車咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:21:21.000Z","msg":"騎馬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"456512dbaf6962a295a1829fedf0479c8ed74221","tid":2089083,"uid":40521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db5f9b66b5a7f2fa7ea3afae3ce471a91c7cf509"